text: Bachelorette Weekend is an American reality television series on CMT. It premiered on August 2, 2018. ==Premise== Bachelorette Weekend follows the crew at Bach Weekend, a Nashville company that designs and throws bachelor and bachelorette parties. ==Cast== ===Main=== * Robbie Goldsmith * Nicole Pancotto * Liz Ivy * Rosa Castano * Johnathan “JJ” Jones * Rachal Smith ==Episodes== ==References== Category:CMT (American TV channel) original programming
title: Bachelorette Weekend
